race.description: Tabtouch Place A Same Race Multi Handicap (C2)
race.comment: SWIFT STREAKER (3) dropped back a level last start and wasn't far away, finishing 1.6L off the winner over the 1400m journey last time out. He drops back in trip again to 1300m this time, but maps for a much better run this time around. Can find the front and take plenty of beating. CAP CAVOUR (1) steps up to 1300m again today. He never got into the race when the race favourite over 1100m last time when the race favourite. May be looking for this trip now and he can bounce back to winning ways. BIONDO (4) bounced back to form last start with a 0.7L defeat when running on from midfield. The wide draw means he's likely to be back from the draw, but Faithfull rides now and if he can run up to his last start rating, he'll can be in the finish again. FAVAIOS (2) needs some luck from the wide alley but has strong claims on his latest performances. GOLDEN OPERA (7) is better than she showed last start and can bounce back after winning here two starts ago.
